ent-MechDSMCarrion = IEE m-V30 Carrion utility mechsuit
    .desc = A quadruped light exosuit intended for light cargo freight and mining duty that has been stamped with the Imperiatoria Eques Exercitus. This exosuit has been given an internal gyroscope and course-correction thrusters, allowing spaceflight. The cockpit is barely armored, and the pilot takes a great deal of the beating if attacked.
