ent-MechNCWLBogatyr = HNF mk.II Bogatyr combat mechsuit
    .desc = A biped medium exosuit intended for extended engagements. Developed by Shinohara Heavy Industries as the 'Jaipei' type exosuit and later modified by the Union Homeguard Naval Foundries for use by the State's mechanized infantry corps. Heavy, but reliable. Can be outfitted with various weapons systems.
