    .desc = { ent-MechNCWLBogatyr.desc }
ent-MechNCWLLancer = HNF mk.I Lancer hybrid mechsuit
    .desc = A light biped exosuit that can take both light weapon and some industrial modules. Developed by Pang Tai Arms under the codename Project Goldenstar, and adapted for the uses of the State by the Union Homeguard Naval Foundries some time after. The workhorse of the Homeguard Navy.
