    .desc = { ent-MechNCWLLancer.desc }
ent-MechGSCMarauder = GSC T-97 Marauder light combat mechsuit
    .desc = A light biped exosuit that has been jury rigged with upgraded servos and thrusters while sacrificing it's industrial capacity. The Marauder-type exosuits are commonly used by the Gorlex Security Consulting outlaws fleet, designed for quick raids and guerilla warfare. Fragile and lightly armored.
