ent-MechSHIGilgamesh = SHI mR-815 Gilgamesh siege mechsuit
    .desc = A gargantuan siegesuit designed by Shinohara Heavy Industries and kept secret from the world. After recovering the schematics from a blacksite, the Gilgamesh-type mechsuit has been modified for humanoid use, yielding in this potent, if shambling combat suit.
